{
  "stem": "444.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The first difficulty was to get the visa, but because I was born in Germany, I came to the United States on the German visa.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "German quota, pardon me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because the German quota was very, very large, but very few people-- very few Germans in Poland that could immigrate to the United States.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I got the-- and that visa didn't cost me anything, but to get the passport from the Polish government, that was a thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That took all the money we had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we payed $1,000 for a passport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was an enormous amount of money, since a fellow that was working for the city or government made about $5 a month at this time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was able to emigrate to the United States.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was first-- we went to Detroit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was working for General Motors, first at the assembly line, then as an electrician.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then I became a supervisor in the electrical department for a-- for a plant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from then, I came over to California because my wife wanted to go to California, and I think she was right.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So I started to work at Lockheed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was supposed to work for General Dynamics, but somehow I didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, they were so strict.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was at the time when they developed the Atlas missile.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everybody-- the guards running with revolvers, you know, and as a foreigner, you feel very, very strange.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because you had to have a clearance from the Navy, clearance from the Air Forces, and I just didn't feel, you know-- feel free.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when I came to Lockheed, I was working for missiles-- missiles and space division.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was the same situation, but more relaxed.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
